    <section id="features" class="container content-section text-center">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">
                <h2>Features</h2>         
               <p> <strong class="text-success">URL Shortening and Naming</strong><br>               
                    Shorten your URLs to distribute on the web and social media<br>
                    Create user-defined addresses like <a href="#">ourlex.com/user-defined-expression</a><br>
               </p>
	

        <p><strong class="text-success">Access Control</strong><br>
               Full control on your URLs<br>
                On/off access by date and time range<br>
                Accessing your URLs via secret codes</p>

        <p><strong class="text-success">Real Time Click Stats</strong><br>
                Real time daily, monthly, yearly or date range click stats and graphs<br>
                Country, city, language, browser and device type such as a mobile desktop click stats and graphs<br>
                </p>
        <p><strong class="text-success">Grouping and Organizing</strong><br>
            Create lists and grouping your URLs<br>
            Distribute you URL lists on the Internet<br>
        </p>

                
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    
    
